episodes.title: My Scientology Movie – BFI LFF Gala Screening Louis Theroux, Simon Chinn, John Dower
episodes.description:
At the BFI LFF Premiere Scene’s Mike Jonas and Anthony Bueno attend the red carpet of My Scientology. Join us as we interview documentarian Louis Theroux, producer Simon Chinn and director John Dower as we delve even deeper into their investigation into infamous religion known as Scientology.
